Package ca.mcgill.ecse321.gameorganizer.models

Class Event

java.lang.Object
ca.mcgill.ecse321.gameorganizer.models.Event
@Entity public class Event extends Object
Represents a gaming event in the system. Events are organized gatherings where users can meet to play games. Each event has a featured game, a host, and can accommodate a maximum number of participants.
